which is...

35:38.840 --> 35:40.114
That's great, hon.

35:40.240 --> 35:41.230
Mmm-hmm.

35:41.400 --> 35:43.437
Yeah, so I should go.

35:43.520 --> 35:46.319
Hey, you know,
there's all this great

35:46.400 --> 35:48.550
