I got them right here.

35:54.360 --> 35:56.112
Maybe I should
send them to you.

35:56.400 --> 35:57.720
Oh, yeah!

35:57.840 --> 36:00.639
Yeah! Real eye-opening stuff.

36:01.320 --> 36:03.072
