making any sense here.

42:33.160 --> 42:36.437
Mister, I'm telling you
I've got your man.

42:37.360 --> 42:39.795
I've got your
boss man, and you...

42:54.560 --> 42:57.074
ED: Well, you know
what, sir,

42:57.160 --> 43:00.198
