I am not a reporter.

43:36.720 --> 43:40.918
He left his wallet
in my store the other day

43:41.000 --> 43:43.389
and it's got
a hundred bucks in it,

43:43.520 --> 43:46.114
so I thought he
might want that back.

43:49.400 --> 43:51.835
