43:51.920 --> 43:54.639
We tell the boss
the Gerhardts got 'em.

43:57.160 --> 43:58.434
(RINGING)

44:13.960 --> 44:15.712
(CONTINUES RINGING)

44:25.760 --> 44:26.750
Hello?

44:29.080 --> 44:30.593
Mike Milligan?

44:30.680 --> 44:31.750
Yes.

44:37.600 --> 44:39.750
