a fat-type girl there.

47:38.600 --> 47:41.592
Not looking for a girl.
I'm looking for a man.

47:42.320 --> 47:45.153
Heavy set. He parts
his hair in the middle.

47:46.400 --> 47:48.755
Look, this is
a family place.

47:48.840 --> 47:53.277
We sell motor oil and pop
and, you know, maps for tourists.

47:54.000 --> 47:55.718
