Heavy set. Red-headed man.

48:11.720 --> 48:14.155
Look, if you're not
gonna buy something,

48:14.240 --> 48:16.709
well, I think
you should leave.

48:18.080 --> 48:19.753
Yeah. You know him.

48:21.360 --> 48:22.509
No.

48:27.600 --> 48:28.874
Look,

48:29.920 --> 48:32.912
