says something like,

48:43.120 --> 48:46.351
yeah, "We're going crazy
down there at the lake."

48:47.360 --> 48:49.192
See, this time of
year not much to do.

48:49.320 --> 48:50.549
At the lake.

48:50.640 --> 48:52.358
Yeah, we were just...

48:53.720 --> 48:56.473
He wasn't agitated,
but that's what he said.

48:56.560 --> 48:59.393
"We're going crazy down
there at the lake."

48:59.480 --> 49:01.676
Even bought a pack
of cards. (CHUCKLES)

49:07.280 --> 49:08.475
Okay.

49:16.520 --> 49:17.510
(DOOR CLOSES)

49:25.040 --> 49:26.155
(SIGHS)

50:15.560 --> 50:16.595
Hon?

50:23.720 --> 50:24.869
Hon?

50:25.360 --> 50:26.634
(GAGGING)

50:37.600 --> 50:40.319
Son, you got yourself
a woman problem.

50:41.200 --> 50:44.795
How I know is, they been
plaguing me my whole life.

50:45.400 --> 50:46.549
What's the joke?

50:46.640 --> 50:49.951
Can't live with them,
can't turn them into cat food.

50:51.000 --> 50:53.469
Personally,
I don't see the value.

50:53.560 --> 50:56.916
All that talking,
and the mood swings.

50:57.800 --> 51:00.952
It's the lack of
rational thinking,

51:01.120 --> 51:03.316
which, brother, your bitch
has got that in spades.

51:03.960 --> 51:08.716
See, the male in the species,
he's got the potential for greatness.

51:11.640 --> 51:13.836
DODD: Look at your
kings of old.

51:13.920 --> 51:17.072
Napoleon,
Kublai Khan, Sampson!

51:18.440 --> 51:21.080
Giants made of
muscle and steel.

51:22.200 --> 51:23.873
But these women...

51:24.600 --> 51:29.151
Even in those Bible movies you
see it. Delilah, and Scheherazade...

51:32.600 --> 51:35.513
I wanna tell you
my own private belief here.

51:36.160 --> 51:38.959
I think Satan is a woman.

51:40.440 --> 51:41.999
Think about it.

51:44.360 --> 51:47.273
With her snake tongue,
always undermining...

51:49.200 --> 51:50.349
See?

51:51.280 --> 51:53.237
What did I tell you?

51:53.320 --> 51:57.359
No matter what you do to 'em,
these goddamn twats just won't stop

51:57.440 --> 51:58.953
till you put 'em down.
(GRUNTS)

52:00.400 --> 52:01.549
(YELLS)

52:07.200 --> 52:08.190
(GROANS)

52:17.640 --> 52:18.630
(GRUNTS)

52:37.120 --> 52:38.519
Ed!

52:39.960 --> 52:43.271
Ed! Are you okay?
Are you okay?

52:46.920 --> 52:48.240
Is he dead?

52:50.600 --> 52:52.079
I don't know.

53:32.640 --> 53:34.199
Watch him, Ed.

53:36.120 --> 53:38.794
Yeah, my eyes
are open now.

53:40.560 --> 53:41.709
(GROANS)

53:44.000 --> 53:48.437
