53:49.120 --> 53:50.394
He'll know what
to do with you.

53:50.480 --> 53:53.154
DODD: My neck.
Something, something's wrong.

53:54.000 --> 53:55.320
(DODD GROANS)
(DOOR OPENS)

53:55.400 --> 53:56.390
(GASPS)

53:59.440 --> 54:01.317
Step away from him now.

54:02.080 --> 54:04.151
DODD: Oh, thank Christ.

54:05.000 --> 54:07.310
Get me outta here.

54:07.880 --> 54:09.837
Sit down, both of you.

54:11.960 --> 54:13.633
What if we say no?

54:15.200 --> 54:18.909
Just shoot them, you
half-breed. I'm hurt real bad here.

54:21.120 --> 54:22.110
(DODD GROANS)

54:25.440 --> 54:27.238
DODD: I can't feel my legs.

54:32.680 --> 54:34.830
Thinking of getting a haircut.

54:37.000 --> 54:38.991
How do you get...

54:39.640 --> 54:41.517
Something professional.

54:44.240 --> 54:46.311
Shorter, like on
the sides and back.

54:49.880 --> 54:53.396
Well, I mean,
you got the bone structure.

54:53.720 --> 54:55.757
DODD: Jesus Christ,
you mongrel.

54:56.360 --> 55:00.194
Just shoot these two and
get me to a goddamn hospital.

55:00.520 --> 55:02.477
PEGGY: (GASPS) Oh, my God!
Oh, my God!

55:04.560 --> 55:05.675
Can you do it?

55:10.880 --> 55:11.915
Huh?

55:12.000 --> 55:14.150
Haircut. Can you do it?

55:14.920 --> 55:17.480
Look, we thank you for...
Shut up.

55:18.640 --> 55:20.153
Can you do it?

55:23.080 --> 55:25.720
Yeah, yeah.

55:27.320 --> 55:30.472
Lemme, just...
Lemme...

55:32.080 --> 55:33.400
Can you...

55:35.040 --> 55:37.395
Can you sit?

55:39.040 --> 55:41.236
And I'll go get
the scissors.

55:42.320 --> 55:45.438
Ed, can you make sure...
Our guest may be thirsty.

55:45.520 --> 55:46.635
What?

55:47.600 --> 55:48.590
Oh.

55:50.840 --> 55:52.399
You wanna pop?

55:52.480 --> 55:53.675
No pop.

55:54.600 --> 55:56.273
I said, sit down.

56:09.480 --> 56:11.756
Not sure
how sharp they'll be.

56:12.680 --> 56:14.432
No funny tricks.

56:15.640 --> 56:20.714
I mean, you saved us
and we're grateful for that.

56:22.120 --> 56:23.633
Aren't we, Ed?

56:25.120 --> 56:27.157
'Course we are and...

56:30.160 --> 56:33.596
You know, if there's anything
we could do to repay you,

56:36.680 --> 56:38.114
you just...

56:46.680 --> 56:48.796
Professional, you said.

56:48.880 --> 56:51.918
Yeah. Tired of this life.

57:47.720 --> 57:48.869
(GUNSHOT)

57:57.560 --> 57:59.039
(GUN CLICKS)

58:14.560 --> 58:15.834
(DOOR RATTLES OPEN)

58:17.080 --> 58:18.753
(PANTING)
